## scss-global
.footer {
	position: relative;
	background: #141414;
    padding: 15px;
    border-top: 1px solid #2f2f2f;
    box-shadow: 0px 0px 15px 0px black;
	.center, .left, .right {
		text-align: center;
		padding-bottom: 20px;
		b {
			font-weight: bold;
		}
	}
	.left, .right {
		b, a {
			color: white;
			display: block;
			text-align: center;
			cursor: pointer;

			img {
				width: 24px;
			}

			&:hover {
				text-shadow: 0 0 10px white;
			}
		}
	}
}